{"id": 5992, "title": "Ticket #5992: CERTIFICATE_MAPFILE should support hash keys as well as regex keys", "description": "<blockquote>\nthe <code>CERTIFICATE_MAPFILE</code> should make use of the new capability of the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=MapFile\" title=\"Map File\">MapFile</a></span> class, to have the second field be treated as a literal and a sequence of them turned into a single hashtable.\n\n<p>A new knob <code>CERTIFICATE_MAPFILE_ASSUME_HASH_KEYS</code> should enable this behavior.  It should default to false in order to preserve backward compatibility.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\nassigned to Kent for review of documentation.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Nov-23 14:22</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/aef81c8a783f4af5202b6df928e17442e7966209\">[49642]</a></span>: Documentation for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5938\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5938'); return false;\" title=\"$F macro should support win paths and path completion\">#5938</a></span> and <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5992\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5992'); return false;\" title=\"CERTIFICATE_MAPFILE should support hash keys as well as regex keys\">#5992</a></span>, version history for these and also for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5973\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5973'); return false;\" title=\"submit transform requirements case-sensitive on some platforms